dc_description_s: The data set is an Iowa employer address file containing GEO data for each location and other attributes of the business. These data were derived from the QCEW programs. All NAICS related to food manufacturing facilities were extracted from the original dataset. IDNR Note: this data was provided by the State of Iowa Workforce Development agency, this dataset shows point locations of a subset of economic development data, including retail trade, information, health care and social assistance, arts / entertainment / recreation, and accommodation and food service.
dc_publisher_sm: Iowa Geological Survey of the Iowa Department of Natural Resources
